<paragraph blockId="57.[151,1437,1370,1996]" pageId="57" pageNumber="58">
DISTRIBUTION: Apparently endemic to outer shelf and upper slope of S. E. Africa, from southern 
<collectingCountry box="[1375,1435,1798,1822]" name="South Africa" pageId="57" pageNumber="58">Natal</collectingCountry>
(Park Rynie) to Transkei (off Qolora), 
<quantity box="[583,698,1832,1856]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.0699999999999998" metricValueMax="1.3" metricValueMin="0.84" pageId="57" pageNumber="58" unit="m" value="107.0" valueMax="130.0" valueMin="84.0">84–130 m</quantity>
, on sand and sponge.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
